# Eliminar categoría
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/categories/3

### =====================================================
### PRODUCTOS
### =====================================================

# Crear producto nuevo
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remera Estampada2025",
  "description": "Remera de algodón con estampado",
  "price": 25.99,
  "stock": 40,
  "imageURL": "https://example.com/remera.jpg",
  "category_id": 1
}

###

# Crear otro producto
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zapatillas Deportivas2025",
  "description": "Zapatillas cómodas para correr",
  "price": 75.50,
